{"tid":27138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入)成都狗慘成活靶　利箭貫體滿身血","createTime":"2016-12-07T06:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T09:32:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3019de0c3a7f38fc1236ba9f5d7e1ca6b00a1e97","tid":27138,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161206184351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20161206184351&d=xp3lZiKZAHy2tdDJ6o9mdxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=25f03361\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_01p.jpg?20161206184351</a> <br />\n<br />\n繼北京及湖北武漢今年5月及8月，先後發生狗隻被當成「活靶」，慘遭利箭穿身後，今日有網民在微博上載照片，圖文並茂發貼稱，四川成都市郫縣紅光鎮某高校對面街道，有一隻狗被利箭插入身體，滿身是血。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_02b.jpg?20161206184351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161206184351&d=xp3lZiKZAHy2tdDJ6o9mdxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=ae991c85\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_02b.jpg?20161206184351</a> <br />\n<br />\n發貼者表示，估計狗隻是被人故意用箭射傷，「顫顫巍巍站在街邊，着實讓人心痛」。該隻狗狗事後已被好心人帶走治療，所幸利箭穿過皮下，並未傷及內臟，經手術治療後，目前已取下利箭。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_03b.jpg?20161206184351\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161206%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161206184351&d=xp3lZiKZAHy2tdDJ6o9mdxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=7b9c60f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161206/photo/bkncn-20161206181218784-1206_05011_001_03b.jpg?20161206184351</a> <br />\n<br />\n從網傳照片所見，利箭從狗隻的右邊身體插入，再於頭部皮層位置貫體而出，而狗隻全身沾滿血漬，神情呆滯。由於被箭插體受驚，狗隻到處亂跑，後來有網民在微博發起呼籲，終於由愛狗人士將牠尋獲，並送到寵物醫院將利箭取出。"},{"pid":"8213a3902260213b060c5877280cf312becb4b5e","tid":27138,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3f47fd371aa62815036172493a1670065650c2","tid":27138,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:16:54.000Z","msg":"甘地ho ball"},{"pid":"43a80045abc80bd6e17bdf40f5956661584f3c02","tid":27138,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debb940cab50b8e22a8e3fa176462b497b215b78","tid":27138,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"唔撚想知呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce52a4cb58454b2622144abc61990f55dd94bb2","tid":27138,"uid":44257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚想知呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啊"}]}